{
  "stem": "2966.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was the Shomer, which was a left-wing organization.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a few more that I don't remember their names.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I also joined one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I joined the Akiva.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was a social club, like.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had a few older guys teaching us about Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a big movement to immigrate to Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- I was what, maybe 12, 13 years old?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to march.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And being taught Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we played ping-pong in the place, and we had fun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was more or less like a social club.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started getting very aware in '37, '38, and '39.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the head of Polish government, the President was just a figurehead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a Marshal, Pilsudski, which, when he was governing since 1918 or 1920-- I don't know exactly-- the Jews were treated quite fairly.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's P-I-L-S-U-D-K-I.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And he died, I think, in 1936.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Marshal's job was taken over by [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I won't even try to spell it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the parliament started passing laws which were detrimental to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the worst law that they passed was the forbidding slaughter-- kosher slaughtering of cattle, because they claimed that it was-- was inhuman, the ritual slaughter.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after a big to-do, they allowed to slaughter only once a week so the Jews would have some meat for Seder or Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Otherwise, antisemitism was growing by laps and leaps, and we felt it in schools.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
